works.description: At the Shanghai Auto Show, Volvo Cars showcased their new design study, the Volvo Concept Universe. A masterpiece of Scandinavian design that’s inspired by Chinese philosophy, the Concept Universe is the company’s most luxurious creation ever, and it’s receiving a lot of attention already. Stefan Jacoby, President & CEO of Volvo Car Corporation, said that the car has been tailor-made for the most demanding luxury car buyers. The Volvo Concept Universe is the first new design from the auto firm since Geely acquired the company in March 2010
